<p>Ok the paladin epic is horrible I admit (Especially compared to some of the other epics- I saw the rogue epic yesterday and almost cried) but I still want to get it.  This post is just to rant at Sony for making it almost impossible to do.  I think you should be able to solo your epic, because what if you're like me and can't get anyone to help you?  Even if I CAN for some reason gather enough people at any given time to raid one of the 2 dragons i'm supposed to raid... they are usually not up.  So maybe SOE should rethink spawn times on these Q mobs to at least make doing epic quests more feasible.</p>
